BRONZE LAYER (DATA INGESTION)

Data was imported into PostgreSQL using DBeaver.
No CREATE statements were used but instead the DBeaver GUI import functionality.
The source files were loaded directly into the following tables:
    - customers_raw
    - orders_raw
    - products_raw
    - sellers_raw
    - order_reviews_raw
    - geolocation

No transformations were applied at this stage.
Data remains in raw format as received from source.